WEBVTT

00:00.861 --> 00:03.830
<i>Previously on "Transformers Prime"...</i>

00:03.899 --> 00:07.334
It will only respond
to the power of a Prime!

00:09.938 --> 00:13.239
Our sensors detected
a second Iacon-locator beacon.

00:13.308 --> 00:14.074
I'll go.

00:14.142 --> 00:17.777
<i>Smokescreen chooses a vehicle
mode with screaming double "38s"</i>

00:17.846 --> 00:20.647
<i>on the doors,
making him an easy target.</i>

00:20.716 --> 00:23.516
<i>I'd be lying if I said I wasn't more
than concerned about Jack's safety.</i>

00:23.585 --> 00:29.923
The Star Saber, a legendary
weapon forged by Solus Prime.

00:33.795 --> 00:39.766
We Decepticons now
face our darkest hour.

00:39.835 --> 00:42.168
I am receiving a message.

00:42.237 --> 00:45.438
- From who?
- Alpha Trion.

00:45.946 --> 00:48.463
<b>2x21 - Alpha, Omega</b>

00:48.876 --> 00:50.544
<i>Forgive me, lord Megatron.</i>

00:50.545 --> 00:54.131
<i>While I do not question
the wisdom of our tactical retreat,</i>

00:54.132 --> 00:55.982
know that I am fully prepared to

00:56.051 --> 01:00.186
lead the troops in a counterattack
against the Autobots.

01:00.255 --> 01:03.623
Counterattack? Perhaps
you failed to notice

01:03.692 --> 01:07.727
Optimus Prime cleave an entire
mountain with a single blow.

01:07.796 --> 01:11.364
With the Star Saber in his
possession, my enemy can

01:11.433 --> 01:14.434
obliterate us all with
a wave of his hand!

01:14.503 --> 01:19.072
I must find a way to tip the
balance of power back in our favor.

01:19.141 --> 01:23.777
Do we not also possess a
powerful relic of the ancients

01:23.845 --> 01:27.814
Indeed ...
the forge of Solus Prime.

01:27.883 --> 01:33.520
But it is useless, except
in the hand of a Prime.

01:38.126 --> 01:45.031
But I might wield that power if
I were to control such a hand!

01:45.100 --> 01:51.104
Optimus, what is Alpha Trion saying?

01:51.173 --> 01:56.360
<i>I wish that I could meet you under
better circumstances, Optimus Prime,</i>

01:56.361 --> 02:01.548
<i>but I fear that Iacon will not
withstand the next Decepticon assault.</i>

02:01.616 --> 02:06.252
So you speak to me
from across the ages.

02:06.321 --> 02:11.056
<i>If you are listening to this message,
then I take solace that</i>

02:11.126 --> 02:14.561
<i>you now possess the Star Saber.</i>

02:14.629 --> 02:18.832
<i>I am certain that you have
deduced how these Cybertronian</i>

02:18.900 --> 02:24.437
<i>relics and Decepticon weapons came
to be found on such a remote world.</i>

02:24.506 --> 02:28.975
<i>Indeed, I transported them
there, not so much to keep them</i>

02:29.044 --> 02:35.215
<i>far from Megatron's hands, but
to ensure that they reach yours.</i>

02:38.628 --> 02:41.810
